(22, 'Chicago Bible Convention', 'The Chicago Bible Convention, led by Fr. Daniel Poovannathil, offers a profound exploration of Scripture. Through insightful lectures, engaging discussions, and prayerful reflection, participants delve into the heart of God\'s Word, gaining a deeper understanding of their faith and its relevance to their lives', 'https://youtu.be/O-8_Jro_oV8?si=Xej-0Lr8gFm1L5jF', 5, 'https://youtu.be/O-8_Jro_oV8?si=Xej-0Lr8gFm1L5jF . God Bless !', 1, '2025-01-18 19:04:29', '2025-01-18 19:06:46'),
(23, 'Texas - Bible Study Crash Course', 'A Bible study crash course is a condensed program designed to provide a foundational understanding of the Bible. It typically covers key themes, historical context, and basic interpretation skills within a short timeframe. These courses are often geared toward beginners or those seeking a quick overview of the Bible.', 'https://encounterbiblestudy.com/', 1, 'storage/notification/Texas_-_Bible_Study_Crash_Course_20250121154605.jpg', 1, '2025-01-21 04:50:58', '2025-01-21 15:46:05');
